# User Stories for Smart Clinic Management System

## Doctor User Story
As a Doctor,  
I want to view my appointments and update my availability,  
So that I can manage my schedule efficiently.

## Patient User Story
As a Patient,  
I want to book appointments and view my medical records,  
So that I can manage my healthcare effectively.

## Admin User Story
As an Admin,  
I want to manage users and appointments,  
So that I can maintain the system smoothly.
